{"tid":1008250,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"VPN 翻牆上網資料直送中國內地？免費 VPN apps 存私隱隱憂","createTime":"2019-02-04T10:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T11:17:40.000Z","uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a245d31944f1593512cc98c898029515b8f8445d","tid":1008250,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:50:19.000Z","msg":"VPN（Virtual Private Network）是在大陸上網時，突破「網絡長城」封鎖的翻牆工具之一。然而，最近有名為 Top10VPN 的 VPN 評測機構，評測了 30 款在英美兩地 Apple App Store 和 Google Play Store 最熱門的免費翻牆 VPN apps，卻發現當中有 59% 的免費 VPN apps，都是由中國或香港公司製作，並認為 30 款 apps 內佔有 86% 均存私隱條款問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2266426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2266426&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=d037a541\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2266426</a><br />\n========================<br />\n翻翻吓牆隨時有公安上門！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155cd2fa175654b454e96c77b4f9a6b327c215dd","tid":1008250,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"有無pc專用嫁"}]}